From cgb en datanalytics.com  Fri Aug 20 04:09:07 2010
From: cgb en datanalytics.com (Carlos J. Gil Bellosta )
Date: Fri, 20 Aug 2010 04:09:07 +0200
Subject: [R-es] Ayuda en mineria de datos
In-Reply-To: <162695.28145.qm@web29704.mail.ird.yahoo.com>
